description: These delicious little cakes are sweetened with banana and dates to make a healthier treat.
name: Banana & Date Mini Muffins Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Bake in the centre of the oven for 12-15 minutes, or until a cocktail stick inserted into the centre of a muffin comes out clean. Transfer to a wire rack to cool.
